ZIQFjABegQIBxAI%26usg%3DAOvVaw1UKh2lAwGZBS-MdeOu1sde%26cshid%3D1570284627721&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=d7d64e08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap241K%402019-10-05T00:00:00.pdf&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjclez2pYXlAhVLMd4KHbS8DZIQFjABegQIBxAI&amp;usg=AOvVaw1UKh2lAwGZBS-MdeOu1sde&amp;cshid=1570284627721</a>"},{"pid":"7cbc3da80cd6e2ce8a433f781a686cd6a915b543","tid":1627042,"uid":97770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:13:15.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"4128f10ba0dafe76aa4c95a6e2358be6952e8d4f","tid":1627042,"uid":97770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:13:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb04df66188889f4c5b81da7265a8c11e7c5e608","tid":1627042,"uid":97770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b04d7a17ab1aaed5d51df723d62c26e22c9bd2a7","tid":1627042,"uid":97770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:13:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f56886e685900537d33b945d9eba979a6f89b14b","tid":1627042,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:19:37.000Z","msg":"聽曰港島記住係和平遊行<br />\n盡量吸多D和理非出黎<br />\n和理非唔好怕無不反對通知書<br />\n香港已經唔講法律<br />\n有不反對通知書都照拉鳩你架啦<br />\n所以聽日為香港全世界出黎港島<br />\n勇和一家目標300萬人和平遊行<br />\n畀人知道香港人係和平嘅<br />\n暴力嘅係政府<br />\n要吸多D國際支持<br />\n<br />\n同時我唔反對衝衝子去衝<br />\n但記住要散水返左屋企先<br />\n避免畀狗圍無路走唔到<br />\n返左屋企之後再係屋企步行範圍內快閃游擊<br />\n拆鐵拆政府建築幫中資國企裝修<br />\n裝修到星期二開唔到門就變相三罷<br />\n唔好等有狗出現就要散水轉場<br />\n記住我地優勢係人多機動性高<br />\n攰同餓就返屋企食飯休息回滿升先再第日出過<br />\n有唔對路就返屋企訓覺唔好送頭<br />\n<br />\n幫手推POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1626523/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1626523/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"193083c80a2a0a54e29177e3e34d578ff8bcb8e0","tid":1627042,"uid":97770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:54:42.000Z","msg":"推"},